OL,5, Rapist police officer David Carrick has
OL,6, been stripped of his full state-funded 
OL,7, pension, the mayor of London has       
OL,8, confirmed.                             
OL,10,FCarrick, 49, was jailed last February  
OL,11,Fafter he admitted dozens of rapes and  
OL,12,Fsexual offences against 12 women.      
OL,14,FHe was ordered to serve a sentence of  
OL,15,Fat least 30 years and was also sacked  
OL,16,Ffrom the Metropolitan Police.          
OL,18,FSadiq Khan said Carrick, of Stevenage, 
OL,19,Fwould lose 65% of his pension, the     
OL,20,Fmaximum reduction legally allowed.     
